data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
Welcome to Facekey's biometric checkin! If you're a geekdom member and are registered with our system, you can use your fingerprint or face to check into geekdom's backend.
Interested? Complete the instructions to get registered with our system and start checking in!

data.name: textBox2.Text
data.value: 1. Become a geekdom member! 2. Log into geekdom's member site below 3. Click the register button and get your facekey id ON THE DEVICE: 5. Go to the device and select Menu >User Mgt. >Query 6. Enter your facekey id and then select your name 7. Enroll your face and fingerprint by selecting face and fp 8. Exit the menu, select checkin and check in using you face or fingerprint!
